data.description: Fantastic opportunity for investors seeking a R-5 zoned Top/Bottom Duplex or those looking to house hack while collecting instant rental income from upstairs unit. Both units are 2/1. Top Unit is AHA approved at $1270/month and expires on 8/2024.  Bottom unit is now vacant and able to be shown.  Landlord currently pays for water averaging $150/month. Upstairs tenant would like to stay with the property but will require notice to vacate if needed.  **Currently zoned R-5 allowing for additional structures to be built on property.**
